This tool creates branch from trunk and updates tagURL in exchange/.*/pom.xml, build.bat, build.properties 

Open config.properties file. Set values. 
1. branchName: BranchName to be created. If BranchName is already exists, it will not create. 
2. comment: SVN Log comment for tag creation. Give [artifactId] followed by particular log message. 
3. antpath: If you want to change ant.lib.dir value in AutomatedBuildScripts/build.properties, Set the new value here. 

If you need to create branch from another branch, change srcURL Value in createtag.bat file to new branch or trunk URL. 
